# Memories Directory

This directory is for persistent agentic memory beyond NOTES.md.
Use for complex projects requiring organized memory categories.

Suggested structure:
- architecture-decisions.md
- debugging-sessions.md
- performance-notes.md
- security-findings.md

Files in this directory are:
- ⚠️ Optional to commit (team preference)
- 🔒 May contain session-specific information
- 📝 Updated by AI agents during development

See .agents/context/ai-context-engineering-guide.md for memory patterns.
